00:05.760 --> 00:09.060
future plans for writing, what you might have planned for the future for any science fiction,

00:09.180 --> 00:09.480
or anything?

00:10.460 --> 00:17.800
Well, my future plans boil down to kind of a step at a time, right?

00:19.660 --> 00:26.980
