As chairman, before I can get back to my writing, and I don't know how specific I can be, the

00:43.180 --> 00:47.400
only thing I can tell you is that I don't think my writing is over.

00:47.580 --> 00:49.280
In fact, I'm sure that it's not over.

00:49.360 --> 00:51.860
The only way you can stop me writing is to kill me.

00:52.900 --> 00:58.960
